item.dc:creator: @ultimatepkvillage ultimatepkvillage
item.description:
@ultimatepkvillage wrote:

Go into your cache folder select all the files. Then right click choose add to archive… it will popup Archive name and parameters change Archive format to .zip then once it’s done upload it to your public dropbox and change the cachedownloader link it should load all the files now
